		<P Class=ENUSCC ID=Source>Narrator</P>
		<P Class=ENUSCC align=left>Thunderstorms form when hot, humid air rises rapidly in the atmosphere</P>
	</SYNC>
	<SYNC Start=5633>
		<P Class=ENUSCC align=left>causing rain, lightning and thunder.</P>
	</SYNC>
